  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375° F (190° C).",
    "Grease a 9x13 inch baking dish with butter.",
    "In a large bowl, combine almond meal, grated Parmesan cheese, zucchini, and carrot.",
    "In a separate bowl, whisk together egg, garlic, and salt.",
    "Add the egg mixture to the dry ingredients and stir until combined.",
    "Transfer the mixture to the prepared baking dish and top with mozzarella cheese.",
    "Bake for 25-30 minutes or until the cheese is melted and the vegetables are tender.",
    "Remove from the oven and let cool for 5 minutes before serving."
